Dialogue: 1,0:04:04.63,0:04:06.85,kakushigoto in 3 - heng,,0,0,0,,{\frz16.98\move(966.4,897.6,880,525)}*咚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.68,0:04:06.85,kakushigoto cover,,0,0,0,,{\p1\frx4\fry2\fscx552\fscy661\frz17.99\move(160,1300,118.4,1091.2)}m 0 0 l 0 -36 l 0 -36 l 20 -36 l 20 0 l 0 0
Dialogue: 1,0:04:05.68,0:04:06.85,kakushigoto in 3,,0,0,0,,{\frx5\fry7\move(199,1110,153,898,0,1156)\frz288.7}赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.22,0:04:09.93,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,真怀念  是「鸡鸡复鸡鸡」么？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.43,0:04:12.89,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,以前经常模仿这个还被大人训过呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.52,0:04:18.48,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,喂  我说过不准带我的单行本到工作室来的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.07,0:04:20.78,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,这…这是私人物品
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.23,0:04:21.94,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你以为我是为了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.94,0:04:25.49,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,把每周画的原稿送去远处的仓库放着？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.95,0:04:29.45,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,为了什么把这儿装修得不像漫画家的工作室？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.99,0:04:31.54,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,万一姬来这儿了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.91,0:04:35.54,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,要是被姬知道了父亲在画充满着大量黄段子的羞人漫画
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.42,0:04:38.50,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,要是被姬知道了该怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.88,0:04:40.59,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,她会封闭内心  不管说什么都回答
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.13,0:04:43.22,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,「有什么想说的事情就用漫画来讲呀」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.76,0:04:46.38,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,要是被这样说了爸爸我就活不下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.14,0:04:51.43,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,即便这么说  能瞒到何时呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.85,0:04:54.18,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你才来的可能还不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.56,0:05:00.15,kakushigoto name,,0,0,0,,{\fade(315,0)\pos(1241.2,915.2)}主助手  志治仰
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.56,0:05:00.15,kakushigoto tip,,0,0,0,,{\an9}注：与日语「请求指示」同音
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.64,0:04:57.52,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,老师为了不被发现  在家穿着正装出门
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.73,0:05:00.15,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,在途中换装后才来这个工作室
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.15,0:05:06.28,kakushigoto name,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,400)\pos(198.4,867.2)}新人助手  芥子驱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.15,0:05:06.28,kakushigoto tip,,0,0,0,,注：与日语「教唆」同音
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.69,0:05:02.86,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那为什么不直接穿着正装画？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.24,0:05:05.99,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不穿成那种松散的样子会画不出来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.36,0:05:08.57,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,而且那样都算好的了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.91,0:05:12.66,kakushigoto in 3 - heng,,0,0,0,,{\c&H16161D&\frz9.276\frx12\fry2\pos(1369.334,958)}作者近照
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.16,0:05:12.54,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,以前可是不全裸就画不出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.91,0:05:14.20,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.58,0:05:16.79,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,算是创作者的日常了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.37,0:05:21.92,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不过  后藤老师的情况该叫做鸡常吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.34,0:05:27.55,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,但是  他也历经了千辛万苦才变成现在这样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.59,0:05:30.18,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,自从小姬出生以来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.22,0:05:34.06,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,小姬的爸爸  在做什么工作呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.14,0:05:36.89,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.39,0:05:39.10,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,但是  有在工作哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.31,0:05:40.48,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.69,0:05:43.44,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不可以问别人爸爸妈妈的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.48,0:05:44.73,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,老师这样说过的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.94,0:05:46.03,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,为什么哦？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.40,0:05:49.32,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,个人情报会和职业歧视挂钩的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.03,0:05:51.37,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是吧  老师？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.16,0:05:54.95,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是呢  不能强行地去问呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.12,0:05:56.71,kakushigoto name,,0,0,0,,{\fade(321,0)\pos(1224,904)}班主任  六条一子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.33,0:05:56.54,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,一子老师
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.00,0:05:59.12,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,切  我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.50,0:06:00.92,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是个好孩子呢  小雏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.92,0:06:04.59,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我认为漫画家也是很棒的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.88,0:06:06.76,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,为什么要向小姬隐瞒呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.17,0:06:08.01,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,话先说在前面
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.68,0:06:11.85,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我可不是画的海贼王和面包超人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.05,0:06:12.93,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.89,0:06:15.89,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,「鸡鸡复鸡鸡」我有读过
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.31,0:06:18.27,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我也是后藤老师的粉丝！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.98,0:06:24.73,kakushigoto in 4,,0,0,0,,{\frz270\move(1628,140,1621,245,2500,0)}复鸡鸡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.98,0:06:24.73,kakushigoto in 4,,0,0,0,,{\frz270\move(342,418,330,510,2500,0)}复鸡鸡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.11,0:06:24.52,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,请不要再提起这个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.48,0:06:26.32,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,后藤老师？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.94,0:06:28.65,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,要是在姬面前这么说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.95,0:06:31.16,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我可不知道我会有什么下场啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.45,0:06:33.99,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,但是  后藤老师还挺有名的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.12,0:06:35.91,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我认为再自信一点也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.54,0:06:41.04,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,世间对漫画家的认知  你…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.33,0:06:43.38,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,根本就不懂！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.21,0:06:45.21,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.50,0:06:46.92,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,啊后藤先生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.21,0:06:50.34,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我从其他的客人那儿听到的  说你是漫画家？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.34,0:06:52.59,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,看吧  果然很有名嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.76,0:06:56.10,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,于是呢  周围的孩子都来拜托我要色纸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.10,0:06:59.14,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你能画点光之美少女么？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.81,0:07:01.48,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.23,0:07:04.31,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,真画啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.23,0:07:06.52,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,而且画得还很好…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.82,0:07:09.57,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,换责编？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.28,0:07:12.28,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我是新责编十丸院
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.74,0:07:15.99,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,读者赠品的T恤做好了我这就送过来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.99,0:07:18.54,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,又换责编了么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.12,0:07:21.29,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,交接工作有好好做么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.79,0:07:24.88,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,毕竟老师有很多麻烦的禁止事项嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.84,0:07:29.55,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,没来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.05,0:07:31.80,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,迷路了么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.97,0:07:36.14,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,会不会是搞错地点去您家里了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.56,0:07:40.48,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,老师！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.93,0:07:42.81,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你这家伙都干了什么好事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.02,0:07:45.61,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,要是编辑去家里的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.94,0:07:48.69,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,漫画家这件事不就向姬暴露了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.98,0:07:52.53,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,姬！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.99,0:08:01.71,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,但是会搞错送去家里的糊涂编辑什么的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.71,0:08:03.58,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.42,0:08:05.58,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.04,0:08:06.96,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,还真有！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.84,0:08:09.34,kakushigoto name,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,350)\pos(204.8,977.067)}编辑  十丸院五月
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.84,0:08:09.34,kakushigoto tip,,0,0,0,,注：与日语「停止印刷机」同音
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.34,0:08:09.96,kakushigoto in 5,,0,0,0,,{\frz6.44\pos(900,176)}风之紧身裤
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.21,0:08:09.88,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,作为赠品的T恤  我带来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.67,0:08:11.38,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,还穿上了！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.05,0:08:15.14,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我是新责编十丸院五月
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.26,0:08:17.35,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,初次见面  我是后藤
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.35,0:08:22.06,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,感觉…位置有点奇怪？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.69,0:08:26.31,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我去倒爸爸那份茶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.06,0:08:29.23,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,慢慢倒哟
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.78,0:08:34.36,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你这家伙来干什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.32,0:08:36.53,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,来找茬的么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.82,0:08:39.16,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,明明我是为了让你高兴才穿的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.49,0:08:42.12,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我也不想穿啊  这种羞人的T恤
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.45,0:08:44.66,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,所以我不早说了要做可以穿的类型么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.75,0:08:48.33,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,在做读者赠品的T恤时
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.67,0:08:51.55,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,作者有时会提出做「可以穿出去的类型」这种要求
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.38,0:08:58.30,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,因为有着「把角色大大地印在T恤上穿不出去的吧」的顾虑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.14,0:09:00.39,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,就有了简单的纯文字
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.06,0:09:02.64,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,随便做的剪影
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.31,0:09:05.56,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,仔细看小点是角色的头像等
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.27,0:09:09.15,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,这样的话是什么漫画的赠品不就搞不清楚了么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.11,0:09:10.82,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,就用普通的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.86,0:09:12.40,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,给我脱了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.40,0:09:13.57,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,职权骚扰！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.82,0:09:15.53,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那就遮住这个图案
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.90,0:09:16.99,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,尽量自然点
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.99,0:09:21.37,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.25,0:09:26.16,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,大人物？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.87,0:09:28.50,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我去拿点高级甜点过来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.71,0:09:29.88,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,姬！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.42,0:09:33.21,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,会被认为是比父亲年轻的上司吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.59,0:09:34.34,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,给我重做
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.64,0:09:42.85,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是妈妈么？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.27,0:09:46.64,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,这…这是什么解读
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.43,0:09:49.27,kakushigoto in 6,,0,0,0,,{\fade(234,0)\pos(364,70.133)}抱胸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.43,0:09:49.27,kakushigoto in 7,,0,0,0,,{\fade(234,0)\pos(242.4,506.134)}大人物（CEO）
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.93,0:09:49.27,kakushigoto in 6,,0,0,0,,{\fade(234,0)\pos(237.333,570.667)}防止母乳漏出
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.93,0:09:49.27,kakushigoto in 7,,0,0,0,,{\fade(234,0)\pos(344,1012)}妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.77,0:09:47.69,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,虽然我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.94,0:09:49.19,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,快用其他的方式遮住
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.19,0:09:51.65,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,糕点师傅吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.36,0:09:53.94,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,钢琴老师吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.61,0:09:55.78,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,主持人吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.44,0:09:59.20,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,这个  该说是脑回路清奇还是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.57,0:10:01.12,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,先入为主的观念也太强了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.12,0:10:01.95,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,够了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.41,0:10:04.16,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我去换杯茶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.12,0:10:06.62,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.04,0:10:09.50,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,您打算怎么弄？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.21,0:10:11.42,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,看好了  新责编
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.00,0:10:13.92,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我这十几年可不是白画的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.80,0:10:16.42,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我是漫画家
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.13,0:10:18.22,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我的工作就是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.93,0:10:20.76,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,作画工作！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.93,0:10:26.77,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,改得看不出原来的角色
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.06,0:10:27.85,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,重新作画
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.81,0:10:32.56,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,画成光之美少女
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.86,0:10:34.19,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,您没有自尊的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.02,0:10:35.86,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是光之美少女
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.44,0:10:37.82,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.16,0:10:45.95,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,今天被问到父亲的工作了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.41,0:10:48.08,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我回答说有在工作哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.41,0:10:50.87,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,姑且不算是无职…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.04,0:10:54.13,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,无职  是指那些没有在工作的人吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.88,0:10:57.80,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,没上色的地方也是叫无色的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.38,0:11:01.01,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,两边都…无职和无色
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.38,0:11:01.01,kakushigoto tip,,0,0,0,,注：无色和无职发音相同
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.34,0:11:03.01,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,姬？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.39,0:11:07.10,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那么  各种颜色都能满满地涂上去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.39,0:11:09.98,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,无论什么颜色都能涂上去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.10,0:11:13.65,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,姬说得挺好的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.23,0:11:16.27,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,今天来的人是CEO？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.61,0:11:18.36,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,穿着T恤好像是个大人物
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.74,0:11:21.45,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,姬还懂CEO这种词啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.82,0:11:22.66,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,真了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.11,0:11:25.24,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我在全球财经卫星上看到的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.62,0:11:27.24,kakushigoto tip,,0,0,0,,注：东京电视台上播出的夜间财经新闻节目
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.62,0:11:27.24,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,这个时间段…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.79,0:11:29.50,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,早点睡吧  姬
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.00,0:11:34.21,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,谁来帮帮我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.50,0:11:36.34,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,猫咪要冲走了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.76,0:11:45.09,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,太谢谢您了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.30,0:11:46.97,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那个  能否告诉我您的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.56,0:11:51.27,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,区区名字  不足挂齿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.02,0:11:53.31,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我怎么可能说得出口
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.39,0:11:56.73,kakushigoto in 6,,0,0,0,,{\bord3\c&HD0CFD4&\3c&H404653&\frz8.172\move(186.933,159.2,132,116)}救助猫咪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.39,0:11:56.73,kakushigoto in 8,,0,0,0,,{\frz8.622\move(705.733,146.4,721,114)}地区新闻
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.39,0:11:56.73,kakushigoto in 6,,0,0,0,,{\fs70\frz7.789\pos(637.066,503.867)}漫画家立大功
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.39,0:11:56.73,kakushigoto in,,0,0,0,,{\move(277.333,712,225,730)\frz7.45\c&H3A4151&\3c&H434C62&}被救猫咪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.39,0:11:56.73,kakushigoto in 4,,0,0,0,,{\frz277.1\c&H677283&\3c&HFFFFFF&\move(742.4,625.067,720,640)}救命甜甜圈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.94,0:11:55.40,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,要是暴露了可怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.61,0:11:58.44,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,爬上坡道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.94,0:12:01.49,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,这条作为区域划分界线的旧山大道被夹在其中
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.40,0:12:02.90,kakushigoto in 7,,0,0,0,,{\pos(450.667,375.333)}目黑区
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.40,0:12:02.90,kakushigoto in 7,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1313.333,376)}涩谷区
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.40,0:12:03.91,kakushigoto in 7,,0,0,0,,{\pos(450.667,375.333)}目黑区
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.40,0:12:03.91,kakushigoto in 7,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1313.333,376)}涩谷区
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.03,0:12:03.45,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我由此改变职业
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.57,0:12:06.99,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,对  我的隐瞒之事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.53,0:12:08.49,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,就是作画工作
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.08,0:12:11.75,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,怎么还不赶紧变干啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.66,0:12:14.67,kakushigoto tip,,0,0,0,,{\an8}湿漉漉  湿漉漉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.54,0:12:14.71,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,您这是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.67,0:12:17.17,kakushigoto in 2,,0,0,0,,{\frz334.2\pos(1051.2,579.2)}愿望之事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.17,0:12:19.67,kakushigoto in 4,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\frz270\c&H2A3E5E&\pos(848,251.2)\frx4\fry14}希望能游
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.17,0:12:19.67,kakushigoto in 4,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\c&H2A3E5E&\pos(795.2,438.4)\frx6\fry16}25
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.17,0:12:19.67,kakushigoto in 4,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\frz270\c&H2A3E5E&\pos(849.6,489.6)\frx2\fry16}米
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.09,0:12:21.34,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,如果要挂在家里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.34,0:12:24.47,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我该写什么愿望  爸爸才会高兴呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.30,0:12:26.72,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,妈妈说过
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.93,0:12:29.39,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,男人的全部就是出人头地
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.85,0:12:31.81,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,也就是变得了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.64,0:12:33.60,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,变得了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.19,0:12:35.77,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.81,0:12:37.81,kakushigoto in 4,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\frz270\c&H51475A&\pos(780.8,305.6)}希望爸爸变得了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.57,0:12:42.44,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,了不起…指的是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.90,0:12:44.45,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,您怎么突然成这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.07,0:12:47.12,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,对漫画家来说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.70,0:12:48.99,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,了不起就是作品畅销
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.16,0:12:53.25,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,说的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.71,0:12:55.67,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,要怎么做才能卖得好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.46,0:12:58.88,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,顺带一提  最近较为畅销的是这些
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.12,0:12:59.09,kakushigoto in 3,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\fs50\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&\pos(1353.6,380.8)\frz254.7}进击的亚人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.71,0:12:59.09,kakushigoto in 3,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\bord2\frz255.4\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&\pos(1904,774)}东京饭种
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.42,0:13:00.67,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.34,0:13:01.88,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.42,0:13:05.51,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我要画黑暗奇幻类型的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.76,0:13:07.47,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,您在胡说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.01,0:13:08.85,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,明明平日里说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.85,0:13:11.43,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,「我才不会迎合世人」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.43,0:13:13.77,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,什么  我只是在迎合姬而已
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.39,0:13:16.39,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,卖得好就是了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.56,0:13:19.19,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,真是腐朽的资本主义蠢猪想法
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.98,0:13:23.48,kakushigoto name,,0,0,0,,{\pos(225.6,972.8)}助手  笕亚美
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.98,0:13:23.48,kakushigoto tip,,0,0,0,,注：名字来源为漫画技法「阴影描绘」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.61,0:13:20.40,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,笕小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.61,0:13:21.19,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你在的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.61,0:13:23.44,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,真是抱歉  我这么阴暗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.11,0:13:27.16,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那除了卖得好以外  还有什么能算是了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.91,0:13:28.87,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那就是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.62,0:13:30.58,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,漫豪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.74,0:13:32.99,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,正是漫豪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.41,0:13:34.41,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,芒果？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.74,0:13:34.41,kakushigoto tip,,0,0,0,,注：日语中漫豪与芒果同音，此处为黄段子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.87,0:13:36.62,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,就是文豪的漫画家版本
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.04,0:13:38.33,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不也有吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.42,0:13:40.54,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,虽然卖得不好但却有着巨大影响力的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.46,0:13:43.76,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,确实  我已经想到是谁了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.84,0:13:47.43,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,没想到你会来拜托我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.51,0:13:55.14,kakushigoto name,,0,0,0,,{\fs58\shad2\c&H102A53&\4c&H103B73&\pos(812.534,660.267)}黑暗奇幻类型的巨匠
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.51,0:13:55.14,kakushigoto name,,0,0,0,,{\shad2\c&H102A53&\4c&H103B73&\pos(750.4,700.8)}漫画家  不二多胜日郎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.51,0:13:55.14,kakushigoto tip,,0,0,0,,注：原型为漫画家藤田和日郎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.13,0:13:51.39,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,想要我教你怎么画黑暗奇幻漫画
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.10,0:13:53.31,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你以前倒是卖得挺好的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.85,0:13:54.97,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,没礼貌的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.56,0:13:58.39,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,现在就有些「稳定」喽
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.94,0:14:00.69,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,彼此彼此
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.94,0:14:03.15,kakushigoto in 3 - heng,,0,0,0,,{\fade(150,100)\pos(1196.8,851.2)}稳定=卖不出去的委婉说法
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.52,0:14:04.86,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,说起来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.28,0:14:06.69,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,黑暗奇幻就是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.24,0:14:09.11,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,画的时候会有「哇」的这种感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.61,0:14:11.24,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,然后再「呜哇」地收尾
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.62,0:14:13.12,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,就「哇」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.37,0:14:15.29,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,向这家伙请教  我也真是个笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.75,0:14:18.58,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,漫豪还真是可笑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.00,0:14:20.67,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,漫  豪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.67,0:14:23.04,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,自己说些让人摸不着头脑的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.04,0:14:24.25,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,还觉得可笑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.88,0:14:27.97,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不要再讲像「漫豪」这样奇怪的说法了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.38,0:14:30.22,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,居然说我是漫豪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.76,0:14:33.14,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,要是变成我的代名词了可怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.76,0:14:35.77,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,说起来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.47,0:14:38.94,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,姬居然会想要我出人头地
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.52,0:14:41.27,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,有些奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.56,0:14:45.57,kakushigoto in 3,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\fs50\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&\frz327.3\pos(1046.8,103.6)}进击的亚人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.65,0:14:45.57,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我可画不来盔甲和怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.15,0:14:47.49,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,各位  你们怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.94,0:14:49.24,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,怎么大家的脸色看上去都惨不忍睹
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.03,0:14:51.95,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那肯定会惨不忍睹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.78,0:14:54.24,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,黑暗奇幻？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.83,0:14:56.41,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.62,0:15:00.29,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不让作者画自己想画的东西正是编辑的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.33,0:15:04.84,kakushigoto in 3 - heng,,0,0,0,,{\pos(518.4,732.8)\c&H41424D&}不让作者画自己想画的东西是编辑的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.04,0:15:04.04,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不让作者画自己想画的东西是编辑的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.34,0:15:04.96,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是指
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.17,0:15:09.97,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,如果让正火的作者画太多自己想要画的在下一部作品里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.21,0:15:09.01,kakushigoto in 6 - zong,,0,0,0,,{\bord1\fs50\frz270\pos(1728,593.6)}画什么都可以哟
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.46,0:15:09.09,kakushigoto in 6 - zong,,0,0,0,,{\bord1\fs50\frz270\pos(368,235.2)}那我就画时空穿梭
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.17,0:15:12.26,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,有时会导致作者因自负而失败
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.17,0:15:14.60,kakushigoto in 6 - zong,,0,0,0,,{\frx26\fry350\frz243\c&H5B4BC4&\pos(1184,353.6)}退返
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.30,0:15:14.26,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,这句话则是劝诫这种事的箴言
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.14,0:15:17.47,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那位十丸院先生看上去居然有些可靠
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.93,0:15:21.19,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不让漫画家画自己想画的东西正是我的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.15,0:15:23.31,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,又不是我想画的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.98,0:15:24.81,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.44,0:15:27.73,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.53,0:15:31.61,kakushigoto name,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,0)\pos(225.6,876.8)}助手  墨田罗砂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.53,0:15:31.61,kakushigoto tip,,0,0,0,,注：与日语「别漏墨水」同音
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.07,0:15:29.44,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,来晚了  抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.57,0:15:31.61,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,真的是太开心了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.16,0:15:34.49,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,欢迎回来  同学聚会怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.91,0:15:36.20,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那个啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.08,0:15:40.66,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,小罗砂现在居然在当周刊漫画家助手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.75,0:15:42.83,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,好厉害  是很有名的漫画吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.96,0:15:44.04,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.46,0:15:46.67,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,感觉拍了我好多彩虹屁
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.25,0:15:46.71,kakushigoto in 3 - heng,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,150)\pos(358.4,758.4)\c&H3B3A4A&}不了解的人会有觉得在周刊漫画当漫画家助手的人很厉害的倾向
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.63,0:15:49.67,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,感觉已经走向人生巅峰了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.92,0:15:50.01,kakushigoto in 4,,0,0,0,,{\bord3\fade(250,0)\frz270\c&H498BF8&\3c&H411CB5&\pos(89.6,590.4)}了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.42,0:15:54.01,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,为什么你会因为这种程度的依据就觉得自己了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.34,0:15:56.47,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,毕竟按照世间的评价
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.47,0:15:58.47,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,出名就等于了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.56,0:16:00.18,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,也就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.81,0:16:04.19,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,为了实现姬想让我变得了不起的这一愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.44,0:16:06.11,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我只需要变得有名就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.27,0:16:07.77,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,您这不本末倒置吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.36,0:16:10.90,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,要是变得有名了不就会被小姬发现了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.99,0:16:15.32,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,卖得好也大概会被发现
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.12,0:16:19.45,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,果然只能选择成为漫豪了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.87,0:16:20.41,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.58,0:16:23.04,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}漫豪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.25,0:16:22.66,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那还是算了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.00,0:16:25.92,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,有一位救助猫咪的英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.41,0:16:25.88,kakushigoto in 4,,0,0,0,,{\frz270\c&H5F6A79&\pos(644.8,462.4)}救生圈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.41,0:16:25.88,kakushigoto in 4,,0,0,0,,{\frz270\c&H5F6A79&\pos(1482.4,490.4)}黑色西服
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.46,0:16:31.63,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,超喜欢猫咪的我正在寻找这位不留名字的人  想要向他道谢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.22,0:16:34.59,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那我们得创立一个侦探团了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.80,0:16:36.93,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,听上去好有意思  寻找犯人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.30,0:16:38.60,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,虽然并不是犯人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.93,0:16:39.93,kakushigoto name,,0,0,0,,{\pos(336,942.4)}古武Silvia
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.93,0:16:40.93,kakushigoto name,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1305.6,940.8)}东御雏
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.93,0:16:41.93,kakushigoto name,,0,0,0,,{\pos(339.2,944)}橘地莉子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.93,0:16:42.93,kakushigoto name,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1320,942.4)}后藤姬
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.93,0:16:47.31,kakushigoto in 4,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\frz272\c&H445069&\frx358\fry8\move(680,670,726.4,592,1350,0)}目黑川侦探事务所
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.81,0:16:47.10,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,小孩子们总喜欢立马创立侦探团
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.02,0:16:49.32,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,根据目击情报
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.57,0:16:52.07,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,目标好像是往坡上的方向离开了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.69,0:16:54.74,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那我们去坡道上方寻找吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.53,0:16:56.91,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,怎么了  姬
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.53,0:17:01.20,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,爸爸说坡上有叫潮人的怪物出没
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.20,0:17:02.41,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不让我去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.62,0:17:04.87,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,潮人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.12,0:17:07.17,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,怎么可能有怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.58,0:17:08.79,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你们怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.04,0:17:09.88,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.96,0:17:11.84,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,潮人？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.84,0:17:11.92,kakushigoto in 3 - heng,,0,0,0,,{\fs90\pos(884.8,244.8)\c&H3A3947&}潮人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.84,0:17:11.92,kakushigoto in 3 - heng,,0,0,0,,{\fs80\pos(841.6,720)\c&H383846&}潮流人士
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.71,0:17:15.26,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,至少可以说是老师我的敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.68,0:17:16.43,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.97,0:17:19.51,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,潮人会去没有漫画的书店
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.97,0:17:21.85,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,然后喝着如同咒语一般的饮料
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.14,0:17:25.27,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,老师我可是好几次在他们那儿吃了苦头
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.52,0:17:28.31,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,怎么办  要放弃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.90,0:17:30.44,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,哦？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.90,0:17:33.53,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,今天回来的可真早  克拉克肯特
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.99,0:17:35.28,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,现在是休息时间
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.78,0:17:37.74,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,店里还是和往常一样没客人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.24,0:17:40.99,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,今天可是挺兴隆的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.58,0:17:50.63,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,没想到老师会是将工作场所选在这样的潮流街上的潮人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.29,0:17:51.96,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你在挖苦我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.38,0:17:53.05,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,当然是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.96,0:17:58.97,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,住在这里的潮人们  只对和自己有关的事有兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.64,0:18:02.05,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,没有人会来干涉  所以才觉得舒适是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.60,0:18:05.73,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,也能够安心去没有漫画卖的书店
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.94,0:18:11.77,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,潮人  好可怕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.94,0:18:14.53,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,没事的  我会保护大家的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.98,0:18:18.78,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那位英雄  为什么会去坡上呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.66,0:18:22.45,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,因为他是英雄  说不定是来击退怪物的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.74,0:18:25.75,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我捡到了一本漫画
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.24,0:18:30.92,kakushigoto in 7,,0,0,0,,{\fs45\frz3.499\pos(907.2,241.6)}工作人员用
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.33,0:18:28.00,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你可真没有紧张感
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.25,0:18:30.83,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我们可不知道潮人会在什么时候冒出来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.25,0:18:32.50,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.34,0:18:37.84,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,出现了  怪物  潮人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.42,0:18:39.97,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,给我站住
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.34,0:18:43.30,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,说我是怪物  潮人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.60,0:18:45.60,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,究竟是在称赞我还是贬低我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.68,0:18:47.39,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,究竟是哪个  小鬼们
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.39,0:18:51.10,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,姬  我都说了不要来这里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.44,0:18:53.40,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,好强
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.40,0:18:54.94,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,这是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.32,0:18:57.57,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,传说中拯救了猫咪的圈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.44,0:19:00.53,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,英雄来击退怪物了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.99,0:19:03.20,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,就像是黑暗奇幻的故事一样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.08,0:19:05.70,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,要是被姬看见我这个样子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.87,0:19:07.04,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我会死一百万次
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.50,0:19:09.41,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,等等我们  勇者大人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.58,0:19:12.00,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我们的黑暗奇幻冒险开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.29,0:19:14.29,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,进到那里去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.59,0:19:20.68,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,这里就是书店？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.88,0:19:23.84,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,看上去有些奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.51,0:19:26.56,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.85,0:19:28.93,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,因为这里没有放一本漫画
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.73,0:19:32.40,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,这个难道就是一子老师说的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.56,0:19:32.48,kakushigoto in 4,,0,0,0,,{\frz270\pos(1667.2,185.6)\c&H6E7275&}在没有漫画的书店…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.56,0:19:32.48,kakushigoto in 4,,0,0,0,,{\frz270\c&H6E7275&\pos(307.2,251.2)}喝着像咒语一样的饮料…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.31,0:19:35.11,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,潮人的老巢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.27,0:19:40.40,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,您点的大杯不含糖加巧克力棒和牛奶香蕉和坚果巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.53,0:19:42.07,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,加冰两大杯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.24,0:19:44.12,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,感觉像是在咏唱咒语
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.70,0:19:46.87,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,快看那个标志
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.12,0:19:53.21,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,果然  就是潮人的老巢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.54,0:19:56.50,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,这里难道是星巴…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.50,0:19:57.96,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,快看  在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.25,0:19:59.21,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,勇者大人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.42,0:20:01.59,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,勇者大人来救我们了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.13,0:20:03.13,kakushigoto in 5,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\bord3\c&HC12C64&\3c&HF857DC&\frz15.74\pos(276.8,619.2)}胡子邋遢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.13,0:20:04.14,kakushigoto in 5,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\bord3\c&HC12C64&\3c&HF857DC&\frz359.7\pos(1552,16)}头发分叉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.80,0:20:10.02,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不对  拯救猫咪的勇者大人怎么可能是这么肮脏的人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.31,0:20:13.06,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,还在喝魔汁  他是怪物的一员
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.73,0:20:16.40,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,所提到的没有漫画…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.15,0:20:16.48,kakushigoto in 4,,0,0,0,,{\fade(120,0)\frz285.1\pos(723.2,227.2)\c&H292439&}没有漫画的书店
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.15,0:20:16.48,kakushigoto in 4,,0,0,0,,{\fade(120,0)\c&H292439&\frz278.8\pos(115.2,414.4)}没有漫画的书店
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.11,0:20:18.69,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,怪物的弱点就是漫画
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.98,0:20:19.82,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.40,0:20:21.82,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,刚才被人丢弃的漫画
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.49,0:20:24.28,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,吃我这招
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.53,0:20:28.53,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.29,0:20:31.16,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,这里果然是星巴…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.16,0:20:31.95,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,姬
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.50,0:20:38.13,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,这是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.25,0:20:39.00,kakushigoto in 3,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\bord2\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&\frz275\pos(1282,353.6)}风之紧身裤
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.84,0:20:42.05,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,在哭吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.42,0:20:45.38,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,发生了好多我无法理解的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.72,0:20:49.10,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,果然卖不出去是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.85,0:20:50.81,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,说的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.93,0:20:55.44,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,今天和朋友们一起玩了黑暗奇幻游戏哟
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.06,0:20:58.90,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我们从潮人那里逃跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.36,0:21:02.57,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,可不要玩危险的游戏哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.86,0:21:03.36,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.82,0:21:04.82,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我要关灯了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.11,0:21:05.61,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.45,0:21:13.50,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那个  姬
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.16,0:21:19.04,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,为什么要写「希望爸爸变得了不起」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.13,0:21:21.80,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.29,0:21:22.30,kakushigoto in 4,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\frz270\c&H51475A&\pos(780.8,305.6)}希望爸爸变得了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.47,0:21:26.47,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我猜那样会让爸爸高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.30,0:21:29.05,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.60,0:21:31.56,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不开心吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.97,0:21:34.14,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,当然开心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.14,0:21:35.85,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不过
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.14,0:21:38.06,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,爸爸最为开心的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.31,0:21:41.94,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,最为开心的是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.69,0:21:47.86,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,希望姬能够健康快乐地长大
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.74,0:21:51.91,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,健康  长大
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.29,0:21:54.75,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那我就多喝点益力多吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.29,0:21:54.75,kakushigoto tip,,0,0,0,,注：日本乳酸菌饮料品牌
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.96,0:22:00.96,kakushigoto in 2 - zong,,0,0,0,,{\fs55\frz270\pos(484.8,188.8)}希望姬能每天都过得开心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.58,0:21:59.58,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,这样的话爸爸的那份快乐也拜托你了
Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,——ED——
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.48,0:22:24.11,kakushigoto ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fade(300,300)}くちびるつんと尖らせて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.48,0:22:24.11,kakushigoto ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fade(300,300)}架子十足地撅起嘴唇
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.40,0:22:30.95,kakushigoto ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fade(300,300)}何かたくらむ表情は
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.40,0:22:30.95,kakushigoto ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fade(300,300)}正在盘算着什么企图的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.28,0:22:36.08,kakushigoto ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fade(300,300)}別れの気配を
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.28,0:22:36.08,kakushigoto ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fade(300,300)}将离别的气息
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.29,0:22:45.84,kakushigoto ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fade(300,300)}ポケットに匿していたから
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.29,0:22:45.84,kakushigoto ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fade(300,300)}隐藏在口袋中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.13,0:22:52.93,kakushigoto ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fade(300,300)}想い出は  モノクローム
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.13,0:22:52.93,kakushigoto ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fade(300,300)}回忆是单色相片
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.18,0:22:58.48,kakushigoto ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fade(300,300)}色を点けてくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.18,0:22:58.48,kakushigoto ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fade(300,300)}给我点上颜色吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.98,0:23:06.73,kakushigoto ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fade(300,300)}もう一度  そばに来て
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.98,0:23:06.73,kakushigoto ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fade(300,300)}再一次来到我的身边
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.90,0:23:11.78,kakushigoto ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fade(300,300)}はなやいで  うるわしの Color Girl
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.90,0:23:11.78,kakushigoto ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fade(300,300)}花枝招展的  美丽的Color Girl
Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.51,0:23:34.35,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,社员旅行去海边还真是第一次啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.55,0:23:35.22,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,师父
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.22,0:23:37.39,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,就是因为包了饺子所以才赶上的啊
